Puuung's first PFP NFT projectâ€•1,000 Unique collectible characters stored on the Ethereum blockchain. Puuung Friends is not a generative art; it is a carefully hand-drawn artwork with diverse traits by Puuung. With new stories, Puuung Friends will appear in Puuung's animated world.
